                                                                            <p align="center"><img src="http://documents.mylearningresource.com/SHRM/SHRM_Cert_Eligibility_2020.PNG" width="684" height="360" hspace="30" alt="SHRM Certification Eligibility Requirements" border="0"
                                                                                /> </p>

                                                                            <p class="content"><strong>Advance your career.</strong><br />If you're not interested in certification but want to improve your HR skills, this course provides a comprehensive and accelerated option
                                                                                for professional development. Participants gain a generalist viewpoint, refresh key ideas and concepts, strengthen their understanding of core behavior and technical competencies
                                                                                and increase productivity in the workplace.</p>




